{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place a bowl on mixing bowl lid and weigh in cashew nuts. Remove bowl then cover with water. Stir in 1 pinch salt, set aside for 24 hours then drain using a sieve.","Place drained cashews and 50 g water in mixing bowl then blend <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b> until smooth. Transfer to a jug and set aside.","Place remaining 500 g water in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket and weigh in potatoes. Steam for <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>.","Place Varoma dish into position and weigh in onion and carrots then steam <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Set Varoma aside.","Add cauliflower, apricots, steamed vegetables, reserved blended cashew mixture, curry powder, cumin, coriander, garam masala, salt and pepper to cooking water then stir well with spatula. Cook <b>15 min\/120°C\/\/speed <b>.","Add spinach and borlotti beans then cook for a further <b>5 min\/120°C\/\/speed <b>. Serve immediately garnished with coriander leaves."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["50 g cashew nuts","550 g water, plus extra for soaking","1 ½ tsp fine sea salt, or to taste, plus 1 pinch","4 potatoes, large (approx. 680 g), cut in pieces (2-3 cm)","1 onion, large (approx. 180 g), cut in 8 pieces then separated into layers","3 carrots, (approx. 200 g), sliced (1 cm)","½ cauliflower, (approx. 190 g), cut in pieces (4 cm)","50 g dried apricots, cut in pieces (1 cm)","1 Tbsp curry powder","1 Tbsp ground cumin","1 Tbsp ground coriander","¼ - ½ tsp garam masala, to taste","½ tsp ground black pepper","70 g fresh baby spinach","270 g borlotti beans, tinned, drained (1 x 400 g tin)","coriander leaves, for garnish"]}],"id":"r145904","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-rskoRBZd1Tw\/XZVPhoDrl5I\/AAAAAAAAc5w\/Bxr9zkex0LUM3b3VacIwUgV0WS83Xu1UACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_8OveImEO3ReONzlS.png","title":"Potato Curry","publishedAt":"2017-04-10T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"15.6 g","fat":"9.6 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"58.8 g","calories":"160